# Build output. Derived from src/, so it is not versioned: the "prepare" script
# rebuilds it on npm install (contributors, git installs) and before npm
# publish/pack, and CI rebuilds it before both the npm release and the site
# deploy. It is still SHIPPED — package.json's "files" allowlist wins over this.
